  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Uganda Population Movement 2018 (DRC)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There has been an&#xC2;&#xA0;increasing influx of refugees from DRC into west Uganda in recent months. Uganda RC have been part of the response to this, initially with support from a DREF and now an emergency appeal for CHF 1.8m
&#xC2;&#xA0;
IFRC appeal -&#xC2;&#xA0;MDRUG040
&#xC2;&#xA0;
BRC pledge - BRC only gave 50k of the 100k pledged originally, as the Uganda RC did not have international delegates on the ground for the response, as BRC requested for the second payment of 50k. IFRC extended the response to February 2020, therefore the final report has not come out yet.&#xC2;&#xA0;
&#xC2;</narrative>
  </description>
